org.jppf.utils.collections

Interface CollectionMap<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of keys in the map.
    V - the type of values in the collections mapped to the keys.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<V>, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCollectionConcurrentMap, AbstractCollectionHashtable, AbstractCollectionMap, AbstractCollectionSortedMap, ArrayListHashMap, CopyOnWriteListConcurrentMap, EnumSetEnumMap, LinkedListSortedMap, SetHashMap, SetIdentityMap, SetSortedMap, SortedSetSortedMap, VectorHashtable

    public interface CollectionMap<K,V>
extends Iterable<V>, Serializable
    Interface for maps whose values are collections of a given component type.
